{"tid":1515122,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲引導方針","createTime":"2019-08-29T04:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T12:52:46.000Z","uid":33267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"88f14fdd7d8ad868349bf4d155fc653b9326dde8","tid":1515122,"uid":33267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:13:30.000Z","msg":"純學術討論<br />\n啱啱岑子傑單嘢, 睇LIVE見到大陸大媽屌鳩藍絲大媽收錢死全家.<br />\n好明顯兩個唔同組織搵緊食<br />\n其實有無可能從呢個方向去促使佢哋開戰?<br />\n循呢方向着手&quot;引導&quot;, 效果快過攪深藍變中立再變淺黃.<br />\n大家討論下."},{"pid":"d397843c812cc8b94802e6d4e18b1a2e624a10f9","tid":1515122,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:28:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1515044\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1515044</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入黎投票<br />\n<br />\n「連登共識」 8 3 1 遊 行 宣言"},{"pid":"218988042de46fc1569403667bb56fcbe3b1bca7","tid":1515122,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:38:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.29 遍地開花 放映會</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 民陣遊行 直指中聯辦</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.01 機場 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.02 全港三罷</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"f6292ca7f8af245498f717116154a712976da1ef","tid":1515122,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:52:46.000Z","msg":"記住，想擴大文宣威力、脫離同溫層，<br />\n要擴大文宣既可能性，<br />\n中立淺藍只會自私地關心自己既衣食住行<br />\n<br />\n文宣方向：<br />\n- 放大緊急法既生活影響<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFkrSTk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFkrSTk.jpg&h=19ae1df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFkrSTk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFkrSTk.jpg&h=19ae1df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snwVMdn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsnwVMdn.jpg&h=58d66585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 放大林鄭既攬炒慾望<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WT8dxUs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWT8dxUs.jpg&h=d3e77a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asdJaF8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasdJaF8.jpg&h=996481da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHbe1NO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHbe1NO.jpg&h=a377df13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 一人一個淺黃、中立既經濟行動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YtJaKn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YtJaKn.jpg&h=c45f7608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nRnrhK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nRnrhK.jpg&h=b96ff78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DK00cXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDK00cXM.jpg&h=2a6e1403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 放大tg既害處，影響飲食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKrq8t1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKrq8t1.jpg&h=91688cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2pwjAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn